 * Purpose         : Declares the component for use in Screen Flows.
 *
 * Responsibilities:
 *  - Exposes Flow input properties for prefill (recordId, nameplateNameIn, reasonIn, etc.)
 *  - Exposes Flow output properties (nameplateName, reason, supplierName, etc.)
